StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetEthnici.es]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
select ethnic_code as Code, ethnic_abbrevea.on as Abbrevia.on, ethnic_shrt_descrip.on as ShortDescrip.on, ethnic_long_descrip.on as Descrip.on from mcriss.dbo.ethnic FOR XML PATH('Ethnicity'), ROOT('Ethnici.es')
